  "text": "There are also some studies that do not show any positive effects of PAP on explosive performance. Winter et al., found that there is no positive effect of squat on CMJ [CITATION_1] . Winter et al. used 3 minutes rest to see the effects of PAP which was found out to have positive effect on performance.",
